{"tid":2172927,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大快活疑似使用內地監控公司儀器測量體溫","createTime":"2020-08-25T02:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:15:29.000Z","uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1dde45ea6e81b43c8601d0b18ebed42f8bb261a8","tid":2172927,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"【大快活疑似使用內地監控公司儀器測量體溫】<br />\n<br />\n『大快活疑使用HIKVISION影像探熱器』<br />\n<br />\n昨天有巿民於大快活及西貢一間茶餐廳門口都見到類似儀器<br />\n<br />\n探熱跟顧客樣貌有何關係呢？<br />\n<br />\nHIKVISION係何方神聖？<br />\n<br />\n「信使報」報導指出，海康威視生產的監控設備被指配合中國鎮壓藏人和維吾爾人，甚至安裝於新疆維吾爾人再教育營，目前已被美國政府禁止進口。<br />\n<br />\n媒體大亨梅鐸旗下，編輯部設於荷巴特(Hobart)市的「信使報」(The Mercury)網站15日報導，標題為「中國『間諜』攝影機迫近議會引起擔憂」(Concern over Chinese&lsquo;spy&rsquo;cameras near parliament)。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，塔斯馬尼亞州的綠黨領導人、下議院議員歐康納(Cassy O'Connor)指出，海康威視的通訊產品不僅有安全疑慮，並且有人蓄意在產品預留安全漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n//HIKvision海康威視 SSD 產品近期風波不斷，它的一款「C2000」型號 SSD 以高性價比幫作招來，被國內知名博主指控換上次級 NAND Flash，另一款消費級 C160 SSD 竟然使用從 WD 回收的 NAND Flash 顆粒，並有不少用家影片實測，導致 HiKvision 海康威視 SSD 國內形象大插水。<br />\n<br />\n其實這已經非 Hikvision 第一次出現誠信問題，之前在就有用戶投訴 Hikvision C2000 SSD 就涉嫌虛假宣傳，宣傳顆粒為 Toshiba 顆粒、實際顆粒為 Micron 顆粒。在實證影片播出後，Hikvision 即時將 C2000 系列 SSD 下架，並迅速修改了產品的詳情頁，刪除了所有的「Toshiba 顆粒」的字眼，全部改成了 3D TLC。/<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：網上平台<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n請讚好，分享及訂閱本台 YouTube 頻道節目：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/好傳媒playfulmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E5%A5%BD%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92playfulmedia&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SblIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=e5a4b019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/好傳媒playfulmedia</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n請大家繼續支持記者報導真相，支持『好。傳媒Playful Media』營運🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n轉數快：<br />\n8292534<br />\n<br />\nPayme :<br />\n<a href=\"https://payme.hsbc/playfulmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpayme.hsbc%2Fplayfulmedia&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SblIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=140c56f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://payme.hsbc/playfulmedia</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVRboGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVRboGC.jpg&h=8f2ad5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4BuUOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4BuUOi.jpg&h=a5ddcff3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b83fce89b8b33a8336951f5d5a26135e27e79f22","tid":2172927,"uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fce248b16905e48a3c085110589cd2bef637e236","tid":2172927,"uid":197563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"「疑似」<br />\n有無確實證據？有嘅先請你發表言論thx"},{"pid":"a305b02436de726afec069e772cd1515fe48ac54","tid":2172927,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fce248b16905e48a3c085110589cd2bef637e236","tid":2172927,"uid":197563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"「疑似」<br />\n有無確實證據？有嘅先請你發表言論thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"97fb0164c893366edbc59c8cb8d9d240e654e951","tid":2172927,"uid":97448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"又翻炒<br />\n樓豬你悶唔悶啲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0e8c0fa0489525ac6d8d304e120bac64c40d27","tid":2172927,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"吓？我都去大快活買飯見到個新嘢，呢舊嘢會影樣？我隊個頭埋去俾佢探熱都中招？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead